main.text:
webMAN Menu has been rebuilt from the ground up! This new version runs up to 100% faster than the original version while having new features like:

🌐 Send to PS3 shortcut to easily send links and downloads to your PS3

🆕 New setup/updater shortcut for a better experience when setting up the shortcut or updating

⚠️ Error codes have been added and can now help you solve any problems you may have much easier
